Description:
TWO BATHROOMS/TWO BEDROOMS in Immaculate Condition with a large Private Balcony PLUS SECURE CAR PARK
The phone enquiry code for this property is - 0528
This beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence with a private large balcony features stunning views of Victoria Harbour and Docklands Park. This property is perfect for the first home buyer, owner occupier or an excellent property investment for those who appreciate high rental returns. The internal area measures 81.2sqm and the terrace area is 14.4sqm, total 95.6spm which is a lot larger than some of the new apartments being built today.
The Watergate building is centrally located and is situated between Collins and Bourke Streets Docklands. The open plan layout offers plenty of space for the living and dining areas and the floor to ceiling double glazed windows provide cost saving insulation while delivering lots of natural light. The spacious kitchen is appointed with a built in water filter, quality Smeg and Asko appliances and it also has a large stainless steel island bench with loads of cupboard space.
The master bedroom and second bedroom both incorporate their own ensuite bathrooms and are situated on the opposite sides of the apartment providing plenty of privacy.
Also included is ducted heating and cooling throughout including the bedrooms, video intercom security and a secure undercover car space.
In addition, you will have access to the large 35 foot three lane heated swimming pool, a spa swirl pool, fully equipped gymnasium, sauna and a communal function room.
The Watergate building is close to the free tram, walking distance to Southern Cross Station, Marvel Stadium and a five minute walk to the local Woolworths supermarket. There is also an array of coffee shops and restaurants nearby to choose from.

Description:
Exceptional Waterfront Living, Look No Further!
Sits on the 25th floor in the stunning Array apartment, this exceptional residence with luxuriously appointed style, amazing views overlooking the marina, sure to impress all sophisticated buyers.
Featuring an open plan living, dinning and kitchen, floor to ceiling windows, expansive 138sqm light filled living spaces plus a state of art balcony where is perfect to sip your coffee and be amazed by the sensational views. All bedrooms with brilliant views, master suite features a large walk-in-robe and a private ensuite with double basin and a stand alone bath. A sparkling central bathroom services the other two generous sized bedrooms each with BIRs. Spacious study area, separate laundry, gourmet kitchen with a stylish island bench, abundant cupboard storage, stone benchtop, Miele appliances. 2 secure car spaces, 2 storages, video intercom entry, central heating & cooling, timber floors. Premium fittings and fixtures through out, this apartment has space, style, and quality.
Enjoy the on-site gymnasium, concierge, residents lounge and access to the 'RekDek' fitness centre, which including pool, spa, steam room and sauna. The convenience of the location is second to none, noble restaurants and bars just steps away, only a short stroll to South Wharf shops and eateries, Crown Entertainment complex, Marvel Stadium and easy access to the trams and CityLink.
* Absolute stunning views from every room
* Luxurious fitting and fixtures
* Saperate laundry
* Top class facilities
* Restaurants and cafes steps away
* Short stroll to South Wharf shops and eateries
* Short stroll to Marvel Stadium and the CBD
* Easy access to the freeway

Description:
Docklands Waterside Retreat with a Touch of Style and Stunning Views
Perfectly situated on the 20th floor of The Quays north complex is this magnificent two bedroom apartment with beautiful city and water views, both day and night. Perfect for the first home owner or the smart investor, this unit is currently returning approximately 5.5% return on investment! With access to amazing facilities and a stones throw from The District Shopping Centre, Marvel Stadium, NewQuay Promenade restaurants, local trams within the free tram zone, and Southern Cross Station.
This stunning apartment ticks all of the boxes and features two generous sized bedrooms with built-in robes, two spacious bathrooms, open plan living and dining area, sleek kitchen with hidden dishwasher drawer, pull out pantry with plenty of cupboard space, floor to ceiling windows with electrical blinds installed, reverse cycle heating and cooling, security entrance with video intercom, and a secure car space on title.
Amenities include the Quays Health Club - complete with large gym, Yoga room, indoor swimming pool, spa, sauna, outdoor garden with BBQ areas, a residents lounge which includes boardroom facilities, cinema room and a private dining area, plus the first development in Docklands to feature a tennis court!
Please call Peter Doan on 0402 959 842 for more information.

A Yarras Edge masterpiece with incredible views

Enjoy 176sqm (approx.) of internal living space plus balcony
Incredible views include Yarra River, CBD, Port Phillip Bay, mountain ranges to the north, and the other side of the Docklands
Generous central living zone is saturated in natural light and includes free-flowing lounge and dining plus dedicated casual meals area
Entertainers balcony wraps around the living zone and is ideal for summer dining as you soak in the stunning vistas
Striking stone kitchen is equipped with Miele appliances including a coffee machine plus an integrated Fisher & Paykel fridge/freezer

Description:
Aqui Promenade: Luxury Living with Commanding City and Water Views
Located on the 9th floor of the striking Aqui Promenade complex, this very spacious three- bedroom, two- bathroom property is fitted out with luxurious extras and impressive direct water views for a lifetime of enjoyment.
Featuring floor to ceiling windows with deluxe window furnishings, a beautiful kitchen with integrated fridge, built-in robes, large private balcony, air conditioning and heating, two secure car spaces, storage cage, stainless steel kitchen appliances and gas cooking.
Explore the luxurious residents amenities at your disposal. Entertain friends on the rooftop garden or lounge amongst the leafy foliage in the sunshine. Work or study in peace, organise a last-minute meeting or relax with a book in the lounge and library. Time your pace in the 25m indoor pool or stretch your muscles in the gym.
You couldnt wish for a more convenient address. Superbly set on the citys edge, walk or catch the free city tram to the CBD, Southern Cross station, Waterfront City shopping, and Southbank Promenades riverside restaurants.

Description:
A Perfect Investment Of Approx. 7% Gross Return
Offering an outstanding opportunity for the astute investor with a lease in place until 2022 with CPI increases underpinning the investment potential and returns perfect for a first up portfolio or buyer seeking a foothold in the property market with an eye for the future. This smart, light-filled fully furnished two bedroom apartment is superbly located in the The Sebel complex which captures the very essence of a New Quay lifestyle - taking full advantage of its enviable location and views to Victoria Harbour, the city skyline and beyond.
Generous living area opens to a balcony with panoramic views
Stone/Miele equipped kitchen
Two zoned bedrooms, one with balcony access
Sleek bathroom with laundry
R/C air conditioning
Docklands finest amenities
Video intercom entry
Secure undercover car parking (1)
Amenities
Secure video intercom entry, gymnasium, indoor lap pool and spa, tennis court, business centre, Yoga room and outdoor terrace and BBQ area; plus an exclusive library/lounge for relaxation, quiet reading or entertaining friends plus an audio visual room for residents use; basement car parking and close to dining and transport options including the free tram zone or Southern Cross station.
Location
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the edge of New Quay with the ever improving features of the Docklands precinct including The District which features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the soon to be opened fresh food complex The Market which will have butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket and Dan Murphys. Other attractions include easy access to the Bourke Street precinct including Docklands Park and Sports arena, Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, leading Universities, trams (free City Circle line), Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive inspection

Description:
Stunning Refurbished Apartment with Spectacular Views
Young professionals, first home buyers or smart investors seeking a waterfront lifestyle with Victoria Harbour and Bay views will want to snap up this great opportunity on the 17th Floor of the highly regarded Arkely Complex. Presenting in perfect order following refurbishing with new carpets and painting there is nothing to do but move in and enjoy the lifestyle. This sleek 2-bedroom boasts a spacious floor-plan which allows for relaxed living and features two balconies, one from the living area providing space for indoor/outdoor entertaining and one from the main bedroom. Whilst floor-to-ceiling glass walls deliver loads of natural light to the interior.
Fully refurbished interior with LED downlights throughout
Generous living/dining opens to a balcony with water views
Stylish Bosch stainless steel equipped kitchen
Main bedroom with a balcony
Sleek central bathroom with separate powder room
Reverse cycle air conditioning
Secure intercom entry
Storage cage
Secure car space
Amenities
Fortunate residents of the sought-after Arkley complex enjoy access to an outdoor swimming pool and spa plus a fully-equipped gymnasium, outdoor entertaining area and golf practice net.
Location
Situated right in the heart of the NewQuay precinct where there is so much to enjoy - with its brilliant access to the vibrant food and entertainment hub that is The District Docklands. Including the Hoyts Cinema and The Melbourne Star Wheel at your doorstep plus a wonderful array of waterside restaurants to dine in at night or the weekend; Marvel Stadium for footy fans or the Capital City Bike Trail. Accessibility to the rest of Melbournes inner-city amenities and transport hub is taken care of thanks to nearby free trams, Southern Cross Station, and the Skybus service to Melbourne Airport.

Description:
City, Water View Splendour!
$1,170,000 to $1,230,000
This apartment is a rare offering delivering spectacular water and city views from the 11th floor of the sought-after Nolan Complex. This stunning apartment comprises of 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 3 toilets, 2 car spaces and 1 storage cage. Featuring luxury in timeless detail, this apartment not only possesses space and elegance, its best feature is its floor to ceiling windows that present a stunning vista of Victoria Harbour up to Marvel Stadium.
Discover a welcoming entrance hallway branching off to a pair of large robed bedrooms united by access to a private balcony with breathtaking views of the Bolte Bridge. A luxurious bathroom services both these bedrooms, showcasing a marble-topped vanity, sumptuous bath and fully tiled shower. The large master bedroom boasts massive walk-through-robes, and a chic modern en-suite with contemporary finishes, ample storage, and separate shower. The generous living area opens up onto a massive balcony, perfect for alfresco dining or a refreshing beverage at the end of the day. The stylish renovated kitchen with plenty of storage, comes complete with dishwasher, stainless steel appliances, concealed fridge, and stone bench-top island breakfast bar. Nothing has been left to chance with special features including a powder room, sleek tiling and plush carpets, a separate laundry with built-in cabinetry, ample storage, ducted heating and cooling, secure parking, video intercom entry, and exclusive access to recreational facilities including a swimming pool, fully equipped gym and communal outdoor terrace.
Other features include
Motorised blinds
Centralised Ducted heating and cooling
Exquisite floorboards in the main traffic areas
Renovated kitchen with Upgraded cabinetry and island stone bench top
Ceiling fans in bedrooms
Renovated ensuite
Double glazed windows
Led Lighting
Balcony Tap
This apartment is ideal for family and as is situated only moments from excellent public transport links, Marvel Stadium, and various shopping and dining options with District Docklands Shopping Centre right at your fingertips!

Description:
Sophisticated Nolan Waterfront Living at its Best
Graced with a coveted corner position allowing for flowing natural light and remarkable views over Victoria Harbour and vibrant CBD, this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom apartment is the pinnacle of stylish, elegant, and relaxed Docklands living.
The stunning Nolan Tower provides the luxury and immaculate setting for this property that will appeal with both Investors and Owner Occupiers. This impressive retreat is highlighted by an open living and dining zone adjoined by the stone kitchen with stainless steel appliances, with a spacious balcony accessible off the living area. The master bedroom enjoys breath taking Southerly views over Port Philip Bay as well as enjoying balcony access, WIR and ensuite.
Other apartment features include main bathroom with separate powder room, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, intercom, storage cage, side by side secure car space, and access to the heated pool, gym and shared garden.
With a dream location, youll be moments away from the newly renovated District Docklands Shopping Centre and Woolworths Super Market. In addition to this, NewQuay Promenade, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Marvel Stadium, trams, and Southern Cross Station are all within walking distance.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

The epitome of sleek, stylish, and bright Yarras Edge living
Showcasing incredible views including the Yarra River and iconic city skyline, this immaculate and light-filled 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom 19th floor apartment has an Array of unmatched features for lovers of Docklands living.
In the Array complex which is part of the exclusive Yarras Edge precinct
North-east aspect allows for sensational light and views!
Full balcony is the best place to enjoy the amazing water and CBD vistas
Spectacular natural light fills the spacious and open plan lounge and dining zone which has direct access out to the balcony
Stylish and practical stone kitchen enjoys a breakfast bar with shelf storage and s/steel Miele appliances including a dishwasher
Master bedroom with access out to the balcony further features double built-in robes and stylish dual vanity ensuite
2nd bedroom with BIR, well-appointed bathroom

Description:
ARRAY IT'S HERE
Be swept away by everything Melbourne with amazing views of Port Philip Bay, the CBD, Yarra River, and Docklands.
Overlooking the marina on Yarra's Edge, sits this sumptuous 131 square metre apartment in Mirvac's sought after Array.
Featuring floor to ceiling windows presenting fantastic panoramic views, this apartment has space, style, and quality.
Offering an open plan living, dining and kitchen, this contemporary home is built for entertainment with the living room opening up to a generous balcony drinking in sensational views.
Just imagine soaking in that vista with a cold drink and some cool tunes at the end of a long day.
The kitchen is a chef's dream with an island bench, abundant cupboard space, stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances, and concealed dishwasher.
Both bedrooms offer brilliant views, with the master complemented by a walk-in-robe and a stylish ensuite, complete with bath.
The central bathroom continues the clean, modern theme of the apartment.
A roomy study / single bedroom and separate laundry round out this beautifully appointed home.
Central heating & cooling, 2 secure car spaces, and secure swipe & video intercom entry complete this sophisticated residence.
With access to an indoor heated lap pool, spa, sauna, steam room and gymnasium at Mirvac's Rekdek, as well as an onsite gym and residents lounge, this is executive, low maintenance living at its most exceptional.
With public transport, world class shopping at South Wharf, and an array of waterside restaurants, bars and cafes on your doorstep, this must see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and City Link.
Other features include
Built in Fisher and Paykel Fridge/ freezer
Built in wine fridge
Built in Miele dishwasher, oven and microwave
Large storage cage behind car parks
Two built in study desks
Italian crystal lights over kitchen island bench
Paris finish in kitchen
Double transparent / block out blinds throughout the apartment
Sliding balcony screen door fitted
Double glazed windows throughout the apartment
